OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'beautiful'
OL,4,Cdaughter, 7, killed in sand hole
OL,5,Ccollapse
OL,7,FThe family of a seven-year-old girl
OL,8,Fwho died after a sand hole collapsed
OL,9,Fon her while she played on the beach
OL,10,Fin Florida, have paid tribute to their
OL,11,F"beautiful" daughter and sister.
OL,13,FSloan Mattingly died while on holiday
OL,14,Fin Lauderdale-by-the-Sea when a four
OL,15,Fto five-foot-deep hole collapsed on
OL,16,Fher and her nine-year-old brother,
OL,17,FMaddox.
OL,19,FThe boy was buried to his chest, but
OL,20,FSloan was fully covered by sand.
