OL,7,FVideo taken by a bystander showed
OL,8,Fpeople unsuccessfully trying to dig
OL,9,Fher out using their hands and buckets.
OL,11,FRescue crews finally dug her out, but
OL,12,Fwere unable to resuscitate her.
OL,14,F"What started as an amazing family
OL,15,Ftrip quickly turned into the
OL,16,Fdevastatingly tragic loss of their 7-
OL,17,Fyear-old daughter/sister Sloan," the
OL,18,Ffamily wrote on a page.
