OL,7,FSloan's mother Therese wrote: "A freak
OL,8,Faccident happened yesterday while we
OL,9,Fare here on vacation and it took away
OL,10,Four greatest 7.5 years."
OL,12,FShe added: "We experienced the purest
OL,13,Fhuman being and we are forever changed
OL,14,Fby her.
OL,16,F"We love you beyond any stretch of the
OL,17,Fimagination. Our sweet Sloan. What we
OL,18,Fwould give."
