OL,7,FThe GoFundMe page was set up by Sally
OL,8,FKrouse, a coach at Plus Ultra Fitness
OL,9,Fin Fort Wayne, Indiana, where the
OL,10,Ffamily are from, to "help bring Sloan
OL,11,Fhome from Florida, cover funeral costs
OL,12,Fand ease the financial stress as they
OL,13,Flearn to navigate their new world," a
OL,14,Fstatement read.
OL,16,FLauderdale-by-the-Sea, a small enclave
OL,17,Fnorth of Fort Lauderdale, does not
OL,18,Fhave lifeguards on duty and there were
OL,19,Fno professionals immediately available
OL,20,Fto help during the incident on Tuesday.
