OL,7,FSandra King, spokesperson for the
OL,8,FPompano Beach Fire-Rescue Department
OL,9,Fsaid: "It was a horrible, horrible
OL,10,Fscene. Just imagine one minute your
OL,11,Fchildren are playing in the sand and
OL,12,Fthen in seconds you have a life-
OL,13,Fthreatening situation with your little
OL,14,Fgirl buried."
