OL,7,FAbout three to five children die in
OL,8,Fthe United States each year when a
OL,9,Fsand hole they are digging at the
OL,10,Fbeach, a park or at home collapses on
OL,11,Ftop of them, news reports and a 2007
OL,12,Fmedical study show. Others are
OL,13,Fseriously injured and require CPR to
OL,14,Fsurvive.
