OL,7,FThose who have died include a 17-year-
OL,8,Fold boy who was buried at a North
OL,9,FCarolina beach last year, while a 13-
OL,10,Fyear-old who was digging into a sand
OL,11,Fdune at a state park in Utah and an 18-
OL,12,Fyear-old who was digging with his
OL,13,Fsister at a New Jersey beach were
OL,14,Fkilled in 2022.JLifeguards say parents
OL,15,Fshould be careful letting their
OL,16,Fchildren dig at the beach and not let
OL,17,Fthem get too deep.
OL,19,FThe GoFundMe page in Sloan's name has
OL,20,Fraised nearly $138,000.
